review.reviewBody: Best Keto-friendly pizza I've had. Will continue to order!

The food arrived cold. The keto burger was incredibly dry and very salty,. The muffin is tiny for $7.99. I know the ingredients are more expensive but it's tiny. Was so excited to try this so hopefully it was just a bad day.
I love Caveman! I've been a fan of their jalape√±o roasted garlic sauce forever. Even if you are not doing keto you can have their ciabatta bun Traditional Burger which is delicious.
Tasty but very small portion and for some reason they missed the protein in my omelet
The pizza was burnt and there was pineapple instead of banana peppers
